5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T09:06:25.000Z","msg":"1. 先瘋狂加水分令個增長率靚仔 D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2. 去到某年個誤差大到紙包唔住火嗰陣，就減下水分，增長率照係 up up up ，跟住同你講去水分工作取得成效<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中国又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}